          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Key Performance Indicators</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <li>500 educators and 5,000 students trained within 5 years.</li>
            <li>40% increase in girls’ participation in STEAM programs.</li>
            <li>Two new satellite STEAM hubs established by Year 5.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>



